name: JetFly
description:
JetFly is a side-scrolling 2D Arcade, Indie Game. The objective was to fly a plane flying continuously to the right between other planes named "Enemy".Enemies fly against the player to be an obstacle,

Player must control Plane and catch the "Coin" . Plane have "Rockets" and player must shoot in enemy. If enemy left play area you lose 2 rockets, If the "coin" left the playing area to the left of the screen you lose the game and if you use all rockets up to 0 you lose the game.
